s.com/resuming-interrupted-restores/\">Easy resuming of restore operations that the webserver kills off (usually because of a low time-out)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/improvements-to-the-backup-now-dialog-box/\">Usability improvements to the &#8220;Backup Now&#8221; dialog box</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/microsoft-azure-support/\">Microsoft Azure Blob storage support</a> (<a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/shop/updraftplus-premium/\">UpdraftPlus Premium</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/faqs/how-can-i-exclude-particular-filesdirectories-from-the-backup/\">More sophisticated options for excluding particular files from your backup</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Alongside this are a number of smaller tweaks, usability and speed improvements, and some bug-fixes.</p>\n<p>The full changelog <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/changelog/\">is available here</a> (may take a few hours to update). As ever, we recommend that everybody updates! It should start appearing as an available update in your WordPress dashboard over the next day or so.</p>\n<p>Not yet tried out UpdraftPlus Premium? Here&#8217;s a coupon code for you &#8211; <strong>blackfriday20</strong> &#8211; it&#8217;s good for a 20% discount off any purchase off <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/shop/updraftplus-premium/\">UpdraftPlus Premium</a>, until the end of Monday. (We&#8217;re sorry: before you ask, we can&#8217;t retrospectively refund you if you purchase without it &#8211; demand is very high and refunds are time-consuming; thank you for understanding!).</p>\n<p>Thanks for sticking with UpdraftPlus &#8211; we&#8217;re now <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/trusted-by-600000-websites/\">the #1 most installed WordPress backup/restore plugin with over 600,000 currently active installs</a> &#8211; and we&#8217;ve got a lot of plans to keep pushing the product further and further forward as we go into 2016.</p>\n<p>David Anderson (lead develoepr, UpdraftPlus)</p>\n<p>T